Switch to UPDATE pattern with RLS policy for DRAFT saves

Added anon_update_drafts RLS policy on form_submissions (DRAFT rows only).
Now uses single DRAFT row UPDATE instead of insert-only accumulation.
Auto-save debounce reduced to 5s (safe now with no row accumulation).
beforeunload still uses INSERT (sendBeacon limitation) with DRAFT-EXIT prefix.
Load checks both DRAFT and DRAFT-EXIT rows, uses whichever is newer.

